      "author": "MsquareAutomation (Msquare Automation Solutions)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hey Monday Enthusiast! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Are you ready to take your project management game to the next level? <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Let’s talk about your Monday board use case! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/tophat.png?v=12\" title=\":tophat:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":tophat:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>Imagine a world where you can effortlessly track the status of your tasks and subtasks in one glance!</p>\n<p>Here’s the scoop: You’ve got your fantastic Monday board, right? <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/date.png?v=12\" title=\":date:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":date:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Within that board, you’ve got items in the board​:star: But wait, there’s more! Each of those items has its own set of subitems! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/muscle.png?v=12\" title=\":muscle:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":muscle:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>In every subitems a beautiful, color status column will be there and each have a name for it.Example working on it,stuck,done etc! Each color signifies the status, giving you instant insights into the progress of your tasks. <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/vertical_traffic_light.png?v=12\" title=\":vertical_traffic_light:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":vertical_traffic_light:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/eyes.png?v=12\" title=\":eyes:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":eyes:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>But the real magic happens when you look at the parent item. <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rainbow.png?v=12\" title=\":rainbow:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rainbow:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> In a glance, you can see the aggregated status of all its subitems, like a master conductor overseeing a symphony! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/notes.png?v=12\" title=\":notes:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":notes:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/exploding_head.png?v=12\" title=\":exploding_head:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":exploding_head:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>This isn’t just automation; it’s the art of simplifying your workflow. <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/framed_picture.png?v=12\" title=\":framed_picture:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":framed_picture:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> No more digging through layers of tasks; everything you need is right there, beautifully presented in your Monday board! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star_struck.png?v=12\" title=\":star_struck:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star_struck:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/mag.png?v=12\" title=\":mag:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":mag:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>So, go ahead, embrace the Monday Board Automation magic! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/crystal_ball.png?v=12\" title=\":crystal_ball:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":crystal_ball:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Your tasks will thank you, and your productivity will skyrocket!<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/c/2cd0bd30fa7522c281ae8963a17ffbc92f9b2a7c.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/2/c/2cd0bd30fa7522c281ae8963a17ffbc92f9b2a7c_2_690x308.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"308\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1366×611 59.1 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/7/f/7fcbf382c116ec04579f09535a653e1d2ebc1a64.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/7/f/7fcbf382c116ec04579f09535a653e1d2ebc1a64_2_690x312.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"312\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1366×618 64 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>If you need any implementation support kindly contact us</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://calendly.com/msquarepro/meeting\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">MSquare Support</a><br />\nVisit us <a href=\"https://www.msquare.pro/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">here</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqidlIIwbejxZmRUWBICcjQ\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Youtube Channel</a></p>"
